    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚投资者如何应对特朗普的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/how-australia-investors-can-navigate-trump-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴尼斯（Anthony Albanese）表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对澳大利亚商品征收10％的关税，将牛肉出口到美国后，该国将不会以相互征税的回应。 Capital.com高级市场分析师凯尔·罗达（Kyle Rodda）表示，市场将不得不为特朗普决赛缺乏明确性而产生增长震惊。他还说，投资者几乎没有藏在动荡的市场中的地方。罗达谈到“亚洲贸易”。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-03/how-australia-investors-can-navigate-trump-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国和印度正在与煤炭的全球转变：宝石</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-and-india-are-holding-up-global-shift-from-coal-power-gem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据《全球能源监护仪》的一份新报告，中国和印度的煤炭动力繁荣正在破坏世界上从严重污染的电力来源的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-and-india-are-holding-up-global-shift-from-coal-power-gem</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票下跌，债券随着特朗普的关注SAP风险而跳跃：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布相互关税之后，投资者急于安全起来，股票资产涌入，而避风港的资产却急切，这些关税比预期的要比预期的，这引起了人们对通货膨胀和增长的关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黄金命中记录是特朗普的关税狂欢Sparks Haven的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/gold-hits-record-high-as-traders-digest-trump-s-tariff-spree-m90jvw58</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统公布了他的“倒数”关税，戈德在每盎司3,160美元以上的新纪录幅度高于3,160美元，对进口量的最低征收征收10％的征税，并刺激了人们担心这可能会引发全球经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/gold-hits-record-high-as-traders-digest-trump-s-tariff-spree-m90jvw58</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:20:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元集会，日本债券激增，而股票对关税的关税低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/yen-outperforms-major-peers-as-trump-tariffs-fuel-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元是美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的宣布提高了避风港需求之后，日元是主要货币中表现最好的人。东京的股票下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/yen-outperforms-major-peers-as-trump-tariffs-fuel-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:48:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商权衡特朗普关税时的石油低迷，金色集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/commodities-impact-mixed-as-trump-announces-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布的漫长的宣布是对进入美国进口的互惠关税的揭幕，这引发了油价的低迷，而黄金则升至新的记录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/commodities-impact-mixed-as-trump-announces-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲资产看到的较高的美国关税遭受了重击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/asian-assets-seen-taking-a-pounding-from-higher-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[策略师说，亚洲经济体首当其冲，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税洪水泛滥，其货币和股票承受着销售压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/asian-assets-seen-taking-a-pounding-from-higher-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:39:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本对特朗普的24％关税的股票低迷，日元更强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/japan-s-stock-futures-fall-as-trump-unveils-tariffs-yen-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统以24％的征税作为全球贸易合作伙伴关税的一部分，日本的股票下跌。日元更强的日元也使出口商股票较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/japan-s-stock-futures-fall-as-trump-unveils-tariffs-yen-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于特朗普广泛的关税威胁需求，石油降低了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对包括中国和欧盟在内的主要贸易伙伴提出严重关税之后，石油倒下了，这使能源免于能源，但又加剧了威胁全球需求的贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
